metadata.label: Note
value: "NOTE: Since printing this book we have run across several recipes such as "Red-Horse Bread" and Pinebark Stew. If you desire a copy of these recipes, just drop by our ESSO Station for same."; printed in red across the Index [table of contents] on page 1.

Table of contents: Valuable information -- Beverages -- Breads and muffins -- Cakes and cookies -- Ice cream and sherberts -- Meats and sandwich spreads -- Pickles -- Pies -- Puddings and sauces -- Vegetables and meat dishes.
Kislak Center Banks Collection copy presented to the Penn Libraries in 2018 by Joanna Banks.

Banks Collection copy contains tipped in sheet of additional recipes. Copy also contains three sheets separated from text but is legible; otherwise copy in good condition. Binding has red/white gingham style flex covers; stapled.
